# Replay and Tool Contract

Apply when editing replay environment, tool APIs, execution wrappers, and related tests.

## Interface Boundary
- The replay environment is the only allowed agent interface.
- Do not allow raw unrestricted table inspection by the agent.

## Tool Requirements
- Every tool call must be timestamp-bounded (as-of aware).
- Every tool response must be JSON only.
- Every response must include:
  - provenance fields
  - explicit queried time range

## Safety Requirements
- Future-data access attempts must be blocked.
- Add tests that intentionally attempt future access and assert blocking behavior.

## Notes Policy
- Notes access is off by default.
- Enable notes only after structured tasks are stable and baseline behavior is validated.
